maintext:
Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Evening’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Evening” game were:
03-04-09-12-13-16-17-18-20-21-22-24
(three, four, nine, twelve, thirteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen, twenty, twenty-one, twenty-two, twenty-four)
